added.title: Monster Squad!
added.description: The Titans want to be the scariest trick-or-treaters in town, so Raven casts a spell to turn them into real monsters.

added.title: Little Elvis
added.description: The Titans team up with Shazam in order to defeat the evil Mr. Mind.

added.title: Lil' Dimples
added.description: Thinking it's a way to reconnect with her father, Raven enters a beauty pageant.

added.title: Subway
added.description: The Bears are stranded on a subway platform after missing their train. But while waiting, the Bears are challenged with recovering some lost items.

added.title: Kyle
added.description: Nom Nom is reunited with his long lost brother, Kyle.

added.title: Icy Nights II
added.description: Ice Bear goes on a late-night adventure to rescue his friend, Yana, from some familiar foes.

added.title: The Perfect Tree
added.description: Chloe and Ice Bear drive up north to find the perfect Christmas tree. Meanwhile, Grizz and Panda are in charge of decorating Chloe's house.

added.title: Paperboyz
added.description: The Baby Bears get jobs as paper boys.

added.title: The Others
added.description: When Anais reveals that she's in the grade above them at school, Gumball and Darwin's eyes are suddenly opened to a whole new world of other students at Elmore Junior High. Gumball is horrified to learn that there are a bunch of characters who are barely aware of his existence and is determined to force his way into their lives.

added.title: The Parking
added.description: When the Wattersons arrive at the mall for a day of shopping, they struggle to find a space in the parking lot. They search for a space everywhere using all their intelligence, cunning and trickery but as the day goes on, the desperate hunt for a space becomes more important than the trip to the mall itself.

added.title: The Parasite
added.description: Anais has made a new friend, but Gumball and Darwin aren't sure their relationship is equal.

added.title: The Nest
added.description: A breaking news report tells the Wattersons that their neighbor is among the several mysterious disappearances happening across Elmore. Their search for clues leads them to find a strange egg, which they soon discover belongs to their own Evil Turtle. The family realize it's their responsibility to track down their pet before she and her brood do more damage to the town.

added.title: Mayhem in Mascot
added.description: After their attempt to get a photo with every storefront mascot is foiled, Ben and Gwen sneak out at night to get their photo with the wooden bear totem known as "Yawk", only to find he and the other mascots have come to life!

added.title: High Stress Express
added.description: During a live feed of the new transcontinental bullet train, La Grange enters the picture to outrace the train, but Ben joins in on the fun and will stop at nothing to come out on top!

added.title: Fear the Fogg
added.description: As Max attempts to get Ben and Gwen to the Four Corners Monument before sunset, an ominous fog bank engulfs the roadway and forces Max to drive at a snails pace, but once The Fogg comes to life and attacks the Rust Bucket, Team Tennyson must work together if they are to navigate to safety.

added.title: King Koil
added.description: Ben and Gwen spend the day volunteering at Repto Ranch and come face to face with King Koil, but need to quickly overcome their fear of snakes if they are to rescue the released critters and defeat the slithery baddie.

added.title: Past Aliens Present
added.description: After Ben stumbles upon a video of Cannonbolt ripping up a computer lab on the internet, Team Tennyson must race to State U to find the imposter; but once Ben discovers it is a steam-punk version of his alien that is terrorizing the campus, Ben must take down the man behind the machine, Steam Smythe!

added.title: Memories of Bobby
added.description: When a pillar of the Creek community leaves, our trio mourns their loss by remembering the good times.

added.title: Kelsey the Elder
added.description: A spat between the Elders of the Creek leaves an opening in their tabletop role playing game, so Kelsey joins the campaign!

added.title: Kelsey the Author
added.description: Craig and Stacks help Kelsey become a real author turning her story into a book!

added.title: 4 on 1
added.description: Onion's fear of crowds threatens his basketball team's success.

added.title: Hotdog's Movie Premiere
added.description: Apple and Onion square off against a no-nonsense security guard after they're banned from the premiere of their friend Hot Dog's new movie.

added.title: Bottle Catch
added.description: Apple and Onion's favorite game attracts some unexpected attention.

added.title: Pancake's Bus Tour
added.description: Apple and Onion go on a guided bus tour as part of their plan to get Apple's shoe back.

added.title: Block Party
added.description: Apple and Onion have to outwit a mean duck who's taken over their building's roof.

added.title: Cleaning Day
added.description: Victor & Valentino gain a newfound respect for cleanliness after Chata's house traps them inside its labyrinth of ancient, magical walls.

added.title: The Babysitter
added.description: Vic & Val want to sneak out to a secret fireworks show but are thwarted when their new babysitter, Xochi, outsmarts them at every turn.

added.title: Hurricane Chata
added.description: When V & V discover that Chata's emotions control the water in the lake, they use it to their advantage and start their own wave pool business.

added.title: The Lonely Haunts Club
added.description: Instead of celebrating Valentine's Day, Vic & Val take on a dare to explore a haunted mansion with their rivals, Charlene & Pineapple.

added.title: Suerte
added.description: When Vic cheats on an enchanted board game, the malevolent characters come to life, and it's up to V & V to figure out how to put them back in the game.

added.title: Together Forever
added.description: Connie has a really clear vision for her future. Steven wants to make sure he'll be a part of it.

added.title: Growing Pains
added.description: Steven visits a doctor for the first time.

added.title: Chille Tid
added.description: Steven and the Crystal Gems try to relax with a slumber party.

added.title: Cry for Help
added.description: Steven's favorite TV show gets interrupted by a magical disturbance.

added.title: Friend Ship
added.description: The Crystal Gems explore an ancient Gem spaceship.

added.title: Catch and Release
added.description: We finally see inside Steven's bathroom.

added.title: Back to the Barn
added.description: Steven and the Gems head back to the family barn to build some robots.

added.title: No Shortcuts
added.description: After struggling to keep up, Adorabat gets a cybernetic "Mega-Mech." But can fancy new powers make up for experience?

added.title: Ultraclops
added.description: Badgerclops gets huge to destroy a towering monster, but when he refuses to shrink down, the kingdom faces a new terror.

added.title: Nemesis
added.description: A shadowy figure named Peace Master targets the Candy Kingdom elite.

added.title: Jake the Brick
added.description: Jake sets out to fulfill a bizarre lifelong ambition.

added.title: Astral Plane
added.description: Finn has an out-of-body experience that takes him all over Ooo and beyond.

added.title: James Baxter the Horse
added.description: Finn and Jake meet a horse with the power to make sad people happy.

added.title: Lemonhope
added.description: Tired of all of Princess Bubblegum's talk about responsibility, Lemonhope yearns for true freedom. So he sets off on the greatest adventure of his lemony life. Though Lemonhope finds refuge from the desert with monster hunter Phlannel Boxingday, he might not be able to escape the ghosts of his past.

added.title: Equipo Monstruo
added.description: Los Titanes quieren convertirse en los mejores del pueblo a la hora de pedir dulces o trucos en Halloween y, para ello, Raven lanza un hechizo que los convierte en monstruos reales.

added.title: Pequeno Elvis
added.description: Los Titanes se unen a Shazam para derrotar al malvado Mr. Mind.

added.title: Hoyuelitos
added.description: Raven compite en un certamen de belleza, creyendo que es la forma de reconectarse con su padre.

added.title: Clarence Loves Shoopy
added.description: When Clarence discovers that one of his neighbors is the grumpy school recess proctor Ms. Shoop - he gets a glimpse of her home life and decides the only things she's missing are some friends. Clarence sets out on a mission to match the cranky oddball Shoop with some new pals!

added.title: Inventor Mentor
added.description: Uncle Grandpa goes to Italy to help a young girl who wants to be a great inventor.

added.title: Jerky Jasper
added.description: Uncle Grandpa goes to great lengths to meet Pizza Steve's imaginary friend.

added.title: Dinosaur Day
added.description: Pizza Steve's jealousy ruins Uncle Grandpa's Dinosaur Day celebration for Mr. Gus.

added.title: Cool Guy Clarence
added.description: When Clarence meets JT, the kid who mows their lawn, he finds a fast friend who shows him some cool new music, a new outlook on life and a sweet rat-tail! Clarence leans into the rat tail lifestyle, discovering a whole new side of Aberdale he never knew existed.

added.title: Dare Day
added.description: With Jeff on vacation, Sumo and Clarence egg each other on in a series of increasingly absurd and extreme dares. But will one of them put a stop to this dare day, before it goes too far?

added.title: Chadsgiving
added.description: Clarence is excited for Thanksgiving Dinner with Chad's parents, but Chad is worried that their unusually laid back demeanor and bizarre customs will make him look irresponsible by association.

added.title: Gone to His Head
added.description: Uncle Grandpa's new found confidence makes his head big.

added.title: El metro
added.description: Luego de perder el tren, los Osos quedan varados en una plataforma del subterráneo. Pero mientras esperan, se desafían a recuperar algunos objetos perdidos.

added.title: In the House
added.description: Rigby eggs the wrong house and gets cursed by a wizard.

added.title: Save the Date
added.description: Ms. Keane is nervous about a first date.

added.title: Deep Space Vacation
added.description: When Gar lets KO and Enid take a vacation to outer  space, they get more than they bargained for.

added.title: House Rules
added.description: Mordecai and Rigby are sick of Benson's house rules and want to live without them.

added.title: Let's Meet Sonic
added.description: When world class hero SONIC THE HEDGEHOG visits the plaza, he teams up with KO to save the day.

added.title: Big Reveal
added.description: KO finds out who his father is.

added.title: The Return of Aunt Grandma
added.description: Aunt Grandma is back and still bent on ruining Uncle Grandpa.

added.title: Let's Get Shadowy
added.description: KO teams up with an unlikely ally to take on an old foe.

added.title: Salamander
added.description: When the professor is kidnapped, the girls must go to a mysterious island to save him.

added.title: Small World: Abra-Disaster Part 1
added.description: After defeating Mojo for the umpteenth time, the Powerpuff Girls are confident they are unstoppable.

added.title: Small World: Stone Cold Spider Part 2
added.description: With Townsville in peril, the girls are sent to the arctic on a dangerous mission to find the key to saving the day.

added.title: Small World: Maze Daze Part 3
added.description: The girls must enter a cursed jungle temple to obtain the last Heart Stone.

added.title: Kyle
added.description: Nom Nom se reúne con Kyle, su hermano del que estaba distanciado.

added.title: Noches heladas dos
added.description: Polar sale a una aventura nocturna para rescatar a Yana, su amiga, de unos enemigos familiares.

added.title: Muscle Mentor
added.description: Rigby gets mentored by Muscle Man.

added.title: Out of Commission
added.description: Mordecai and Rigby have one last day with the cart before they have to get rid of it.

added.title: Prankless
added.description: The guys want to win a prank war with a rival park.

added.title: El Arbol Perfecto
added.description: Chloe y Polar conducen hacia el norte para encontrar el árbol de Navidad perfecto. Mientras tanto, Pardo y Panda quedan a cargo de la decoración de la casa de Chloe.

added.title: Osos Repartidores
added.description: Los ositos comienzan a trabajar de repartidores de periódicos.

added.title: Truth
added.description: An old Plumber partner of Max's resurfaces with nefarious intentions and ends up stealing the dangerous Null Void Projector.

added.title: Framed
added.description: Kevin 11 is back and out for revenge. And with the ability to shape-shift into several of Ben's alien heroes, he's been framing Ben for his crimes.

added.title: Kelsey la Anciana
added.description: Una discusión entre los Ancianos del Arroyo deja un lugar vacante en su juego de rol de mesa, así que Kelsey se une a la campaña.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Desastre en Mascota
added.description: Frustrado su intento de conseguir una foto con cada mascota de vidriera, Ben y Gwen se escabullen de noche para tomarse su foto con el tótem del oso de madera... iy descubren que él y las demás mascotas cobraron vida!

added.title: Expreso De Gran Estres
added.description: Durante una transmisión en vivo del nuevo tren bala transcontinental, La Grange se cuela para ganarle al tren. Pero Ben se suma a la diversión, iy no se detendrá ante nada para salir victorioso!

added.title: Kelsey la autora
added.description: iCraig y Stacks ayudan a Kelsey a convertirse en una verdadera autora al convertir su historia en un libro!
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Teman a la Niebla
added.description: Mientras Max intenta llevar a Ben y Gwen al Monumento de las Cuatro Esquinas antes del atardecer, un banco de niebla siniestra envuelve la carretera y obliga a Max a conducir a la velocidad de un caracol. Pero una vez que Fogg cobra vida y ataca el Rust Bucket, el equipo Tennyson debe trabajar unido si se quieren llegar sanos y salvos.

added.title: Rey Koil
added.description: Ben y Gwen pasan el día como voluntarios en Repto Ranch y se enfrentan cara a cara con el Rey Koil. Pero necesitan superar rápidamente su miedo a las serpientes si quieren rescatar a las criaturas liberadas y derrotar al serpenteante villano.

added.title: Alienigenas del Pasado, Presente
added.description: Cuando Ben encuentra un video en Internet en el que Cannonbolt destruye un laboratorio informático, el equipo Tennyson debe correr a State U para encontrar al impostor. Pero una vez que Ben descubra que una versión a vapor de su alienígena es la que está aterrorizando al campus, deberá derribar al hombre que está detrás de la máquina: iVapor Smythe!

added.title: Rad's Alien Sickness
added.description: When our heroes are infected with a virus, Rad stubbornly refuses to back down.

added.title: Dia de limpieza
added.description: Victor y Valentino adquieren un nuevo respeto por la limpieza después de que la casa de Chata los atrapa dentro de su laberinto de paredes antiguas y mágicas.

added.title: 4 a 1
added.description: El temor de Cebollín a las multitudes amenaza el éxito de su equipo de baloncesto.

added.title: La ninera
added.description: Vic y Val quieren colarse en un espectáculo secreto de fuegos artificiales, pero su plan se ve frustrado cuando su nueva niñera, Xochi, los supera en todo momento.

added.title: Hot Dog Estrena su Pelicula
added.description: Cuando unos guardias de seguridad muy serios los echan del estreno de la nueva película de su amigo Hot Dog, Manzana y Cebollín se preparan para pelear.

added.title: Atrapa la Botella
added.description: Manzana y Cebollín inventan un nuevo juego que atrae una atención inesperada.

added.title: Huracan Chata
added.description: Cuando V y V descubren que las emociones de Chata controlan el agua del lago, deciden sacar ventaja y comienzan su propio negocio de piscinas de olas.

added.title: Loteria
added.description: Cuando Vic hace trampa en un juego de mesa encantado, los malvados personajes cobran vida, y V y V son los responsables de averiguar cómo volver a ponerlos en el juego.

added.title: El Paseo en Autobus de Pancake
added.description: Manzana y Cebollín suben a un autobús que da un tour guiado como parte de su plan para recuperar el zapato de Manzana.

added.title: El club de los solitarios
added.description: En lugar de celebrar el Día de San Valentín, Vic y Val se atreven a explorar una mansión encantada con sus rivales, Charlene y Piña.

added.title: Fiesta en la Cuadra
added.description: Manzana y Cebollín deben ser más astutos que un pato malvado que se apoderó del techo de su edificio.

added.title: Lucky Girl
added.description: Ben battles an evil sorcerer whose power whose emanates from mystic charms, one of which turns Gwen into her own superhero named Lucky Girl.

added.title: Arrested Development
added.description: Ben and Rook must stop the evil Robots from Dimension 12 while trapped in their own pre-pubescent bodies, thanks to Ben's childhood rival.  (Introducing Billy Billions.)

added.title: Ben Again
added.description: When Eon causes 11-year old Ben swap minds with teen Ben, it's up to Gwen, Rook, and Professor Paradox to set things straight.  (Featuring Eon and Professor Paradox.)

added.title: Hoofin' It
added.description: It's time for the annual Aberdale Greased Pig Chase and everyone's excited except Clarence. He feels so bad for poor little pig Butterscotch that he takes her place in the pig chase, running from townsfolk eager to take home the prized barrel full of hot dogs!

added.title: Bengeance is Mine
added.description: Vilgax' former lackey Psyphon is elated when his master returns.

added.title: Animo Crackers
added.description: Dr. Animo from the future comes back to the present to help himself defeat Ben once and for all. (Introducing new Ben alien, Gutrot.)

added.title: And Then There Were None
added.description: Vilgax and Eon team up to wipe out every Ben in every dimension!

added.title: Duele Crecer
added.description: Steven va al médico por primera vez.

added.title: Sin Atajos
added.description: Tras esforzarse por mantener el ritmo en las batallas, Adorabat consigue una armadura cibernética. ¿Pero podrán unos nuevos y sofisticados poderes compensar la falta de experiencia?

added.title: Juntos por Siempre
added.description: Connie tiene una visión muy clara de su futuro, y Steven quiere asegurarse de ser parte de esa visión.

added.title: Ultracolosal
added.description: Colosal se vuelve enorme para destruir a un monstruo altísimo, pero cuando se rehúsa a volver a su tamaño normal, el reino se enfrenta a un nuevo terror… el apetito insaciable de Colosal.

removed.title: Not So Secret Service
